if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點都好啦，唔好再做水魚。<br />\n<br />\n如果自己明知自己真係控制唔到<br />\n搵方法自己幫自己已經係一種進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00011b62051188aa1d4f761cf4bc1ff859554242","tid":1899741,"uid":167828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T23:12:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc2077457da0e57e4a1fedd11e6e29b79d0d1eee","tid":1899741,"uid":119361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T23:29:28.000Z","msg":"破產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d620e4deb33604d9e79a586b35c687664fff7c4","tid":1899741,"uid":197074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T23:32:18.000Z","msg":"點解係兼職？"},{"pid":"4c7eac11a5a2fbdb5607a632180cd0b813182107","tid":1899741,"uid":247338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20c357dc601760e6f36b58ab0ee336598d907a7f","tid":1899741,"uid":36049,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"7736db3ada8dfff4017285b0b20d0cce2828d69d","tid":1899741,"uid":141630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T19:46:38.000Z","msg":"街數？<br />\n賭錢定咩原因先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T20:12:09.000Z","msg":"呢d case 99%賭錢架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n信d fb 賭錢page 幾個鐘五萬果d <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T23:34:31.000Z","msg":"果班友賣倫敦金"},{"pid":"9b5536763c24d6bfa61d9a5fb0bafa64e466b69c","tid":1899741,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T23:34:47.000Z","msg":"信巴菲特得永生"},{"pid":"77b3a8c7137f6f28ebf7f7d4